OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome brightness at first, but cloud
OL,7,Fand rain spread west into Orkney
OL,8,Fthrough the evening, reaching Shetland
OL,9,Fovernight. Clearer spells and blustery
OL,10,Fshowers arriving by morning across
OL,11,FOrkney.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloud and rain soon clearing
OL,14,FShetland. Otherwise bright or sunny
OL,15,Fspells and scattered showers. Drier
OL,16,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Blustery
OL,17,Fwest to northwest winds, easing in the
OL,18,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
