OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,6,Fcold with sunny spells and scattered
OL,7,Fheavy showers through Wednesday and
OL,8,FThursday. Breezy at times on Thursday.
OL,9,FMostly dry and bright Friday, but the
OL,10,Fodd shower possible first thing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
